{"tid":2365684,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"好文重溫 whatsapp PR","createTime":"2021-01-14T03:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T03:51:45.000Z","uid":306614,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6710ba548d98e7625eff0c48da399061ee1cdfd0","tid":2365684,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"幫手傳<br />\n手動轉發-<br />\n<br />\n最近見好多朋友講緊由WhatsApp轉會Signal<br />\n當年，小弟響香港某廣告公司工作<br />\n曾經負責Line嘅網絡宣傳工作<br />\n<br />\n今日想同大家分享一下<br />\n當年我接觸到嘅競爭對手WhatsApp<br />\n佢地嘅網絡言論策略，<br />\n睇睇佢地多年來<br />\n每一次有競爭對手出現都會採用嘅戰略<br />\n<br />\n香港自2008年，<br />\n曾令WhatsApp產生危機感而有動作嘅<br />\n包括Line，WeChat，以及而家嘅Signal<br />\n<br />\n而每次，<br />\nWhatsApp所使用嘅策略都係同一套<br />\n包括淡化、抹黑、製造混亂<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp作為香港人慣性使用嘅通訊軟件<br />\n佢地無需要響網絡上贏出任何辯論<br />\n佢地嘅目的只有一個<br />\n就係「製造資訊疲勞」<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp非常清楚香港人<br />\n「怕麻煩」、「三分鐘熱度」特性<br />\n只要令大量資訊持續轟炸<br />\n（包括網絡上嘅罵戰，大量資訊湧現）<br />\n大部份網民都會響新鮮感下降<br />\n以及唔想再睇呢d情緒下<br />\n選擇繼續用返「慣性使用」嘅WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n而事實亦證明，當年Line敗仗<br />\n係因為正、反、持平三方大混戰<br />\n大量網民對於資訊混亂無法理出頭緒或結論<br />\n最終選擇「唔轉會」，「用返WhatsApp算啦」<br />\n<br />\n而至於WeChat，<br />\n當年雖然有Big4廣告同演唱會聲勢浩大<br />\n甚至響海底隧道出口放出大型廣告牌，<br />\n聲勢一時無兩<br />\n但WhatsApp以遠低於廣告牌價錢<br />\n響討論區製造混亂<br />\n配合幾個討論區網民對大陸嘅反感<br />\n要維持WhatsApp於霸權實在易如反掌<br />\n<br />\n接下來，本人預計，<br />\nWhatsApp已經開始第一階段「淡化」手段<br />\n本港網絡上已經開始出現「Signal亦有問題」<br />\n以及「WhatsApp做法跟其他產品差不多<br />\n呢一類嘅講法<br />\n<br />\n稍後時間，高登連登等討論區，<br />\n將會出現大量有關Signal的不利新聞，<br />\n假新聞以及罵戰出現<br />\n呢一切響2月8日WhatsApp新Policy生效前<br />\n將會到達頂峰，令部份人跌落去<br />\n「算啦，Click同意WhatsApp嘅Policy」諗法<br />\n<br />\n假若各位真心唔希望霸權繼續<br />\n唔希望被PR公司左右，放棄你嘅私隱安全<br />\n請認清WhatsApp公司手段<br />\n並時刻保持初心，堅持到底<br />\n各位加油！"},{"pid":"b3e2024f676fbd2cc171707ab485e8b867896ee4","tid":2365684,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3939389c97423898d82834fb538d090ec4ef35fd","tid":2365684,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bc052dfc3338110a166395b30821d8d9df1bc4","tid":2365684,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"Line 本身又lag 又慢<br />\n無人用正常啦屌你"},{"pid":"186ad786978d908425cea72da06d08fa39752fce","tid":2365684,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2349d0b1948bdd842bfa89b7a0c0c294aa46363","tid":2365684,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90bc052dfc3338110a166395b30821d8d9df1bc4","tid":2365684,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"Line 本身又lag 又慢<br />\n無人用正常啦屌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:23:41.000Z","msg":"不嬲用開line冇試過以上問題<br />\n反而WhatsApp 成日比人強制加左入D補習投資群組<br />\n檢舉又冇人理，極度懷疑係WhatsApp 自己攪出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c998daab3c54019b9b5899bdf3e7b8bb72382b","tid":2365684,"uid":249866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286c025f5822f595f7abf0895bad4e76fab81079","tid":2365684,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2349d0b1948bdd842bfa89b7a0c0c294aa46363","tid":2365684,"uid":321374,"lik